# Privacy Policy

**Lensiary – Contact Lens Manager & Tracker**

**Effective Date:** 19 July 2026

Thank you for using **Lensiary** ("the App"). Your privacy is important to us. Lensiary has been designed with a privacy-first approach, keeping your personal information on your device wherever possible.

This Privacy Policy explains what information the App collects, how it is used, and how it is protected.

By using Lensiary, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

